<plot>Eight-year-old Li Tong from Beijing loses her bus pass one day after school. She decides to walk home. On her way, she encounters a warm-hearted old lady, a security guard, a young woman, a man wearing a panda costume, and even a little thief. She soon finds herself hopelessly lost. Only a boy her age, who doesn't go to school but really knows his way around Beijing, offers her a helping hand.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?334360</url></doc>
